graph TD
    Start[Identificar Necessidade Técnica] --> Research[Pesquisar Alternativas]
    Research --> Impact{Alto Impacto?}
    
    Impact -- Sim --> RFC[Escrever RFC]
    RFC --> Discussion[Debate no Time/Review]
    Discussion --> ADR[Gerar ADR - Architecture Decision Record]
    ADR --> Registry[Registrar em .specs/architecture/]
    Registry --> Implementation[Iniciar SDD]
    
    Impact -- Não --> Documentation[Nota Rápida em MEMORY.md]
    Documentation --> Implementation
    
    subgraph SDD_Flow
        Implementation --> Spec[spec.md]
        Spec --> Plan[plan.md]
        Plan --> Code[Executar Tasks]
    end

    style ADR fill:#f96,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RFC fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style SDD_Flow fill:#eee,stroke:#999,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
